<small>[<a href="/ideas/paint.pl?oek_parent=1212&amp;oek_painter=shi_norm&amp;oek_x=400&amp;oek_y=259&amp;oek_src=/en/arch/src/1237835591548.jpg">Oekaki</a>]</small>
<br />

				
